{"tid":2229150,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你被之鋒罵 為什麼不說他五毛 為什麼不說他PR？","createTime":"2020-10-04T07:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T02:02:52.000Z","uid":73381,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"312c73bdb60c50433f73cdd9005dd6e04efbec65","tid":2229150,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"主唱：章魚咀(章)&amp;下亞XX道(下)<br />\n<br />\n直到片上載 你才懂得去連登回應每個<br />\n批評貼文 人血九大鬼搞事<br />\n<br />\n直到你後悔 之鋒已經開po對你恥笑<br />\n嬲爆的你 開始了一段掙扎<br />\n<br />\n下：<br />\n你被之鋒罵 <br />\n為什麼不說他五毛<br />\n為什麼不說他PR <br />\n你章魚咀<br />\n這是每個人都知道啊<br />\n<br />\n章：<br />\n你被之鋒罵 為什麼要忍聲吞下<br />\n是不是健吾劉正又搞分化<br />\n所以你不斷重覆留言 無法解答<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7f43b399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"60dabbf5e1e5ac512c60f260ec9ded8cda72b410","tid":2229150,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"192f516bf89e8ad86a62cef01eca85bd10e63a99","tid":2229150,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4e3792fc6d3872cfb6a98f633b322153c81ddf","tid":2229150,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"幫下哥答埋先<br />\n<br />\n原來係輔仁狗挑引事端，想分化兩邊，唔怪得健吾，劉正 react 咁快但容樂其唔出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成堆垃圾 account 出曬黎，兩個唔同路線互相批評下抽下水好正常，但有人想製造對立就好明顯搞分化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d52f2df45d3d0ebc9dad1dd1abcbc93f9103190","tid":2229150,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60dabbf5e1e5ac5